{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"dependencies vs. devDependencies","date":"2023-02-14","slug":"2023-02-14-dependencies","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>package.json에 있는 dependencies와 devDependencies의 차이</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>dependencies</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>실제 런타임에서 사용되는 라이브러리</li>\n<li>배포할 때 포함</li>\n<li>axios, react, vue 등</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>설치 방법</h2>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">$</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">npm</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">install</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">라이브러리명</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h1>devDependencies</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>개발자가 <strong>개발할 때만 필요한 라이브러리</strong>로, 로컬 개발 또는 테스트에 사용</li>\n<li>배포할 때 포함되지 않음</li>\n<li>컴파일 도구(gulp, webpack, …), babel, eslint, prettier 등</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>설치 방법</h2>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">$</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">npm</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">install</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">라이브러리명</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">--save-dev</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">$</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">npm</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">install</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">라이브러리명</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">-D</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h1>구분하는 이유</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>빌드 시간 및 어플리케이션 크기를 줄이기 위함</li>\n</ul>"}},"__N_SSG":true}